com.tomzhu.tree

Class AVLTreeNode<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomzhu.tree.AVLTreeNode<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of element.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tree

    public class AVLTreeNode<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tree
    AVLTreeNode represent a node of AVL tree. we redefine a tree node class here but doesn't use the binary tree node, the reason is that a avl tree node has an element called height.
    Since:
    1.7
    Author:
    tomzhu
